{"tid":665044,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗有隱睪症","createTime":"2018-05-14T14:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T15:27:14.000Z","uid":185792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"62f06235ff87945c61530f262413c1791001eecf","tid":665044,"uid":185792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:56:53.000Z","msg":"我隻狗狗已經8歲 琴日去左新地方剪毛<br />\n個姐姐話我知 狗狗係隱睪丸<br />\n因為以前唔識諗 無幫佢絕育<br />\n想問下各位巴絲<br />\n元朗有無做呢個隱睪絕育手術嘅好獸醫推介？<br />\n我仲好猶豫 好唔好做呢個手術<br />\n好驚搵到個唔好嘅獸醫<br />\n狗狗8歲 咁遲先捱呢刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7240e21004e8926f0234db89c387976bcdc39c3b","tid":665044,"uid":19214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"乜野係隱睪症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c2dc853edbcd69d87fa12bbb6213dae587ce44","tid":665044,"uid":185792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7240e21004e8926f0234db89c387976bcdc39c3b","tid":665044,"uid":19214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"乜野係隱睪症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;雄犬在出生之前，睪丸多已從腹腔下降到陰囊，但有些是出生1-2周後甚至10周後才下降。<br />\n但有些犬隻可能會延遲到五或六個月齡，睪丸才降到陰囊內。個體差異算是蠻大的。幼犬若屆六月齡(但有文獻認為是三個月)而睪丸尚未下降到陰囊內，則再要降下的可能性就不高。<br />\n因此保守建議以六月齡，睪丸有無下降到陰囊來診斷是否為隱睪。約有６～１２％公狗有隱睪症。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，狗狗無絕到育，但蛋蛋隱藏喺身體入面，無跌出黎"},{"pid":"48fe083e8bd0780c224a1fbe5c80a957f7347e74","tid":665044,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:09:27.000Z","msg":"唔做有乜影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf9dd9a5fa9956aad9148943a7586b4b6176084","tid":665044,"uid":185792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48fe083e8bd0780c224a1fbe5c80a957f7347e74","tid":665044,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:09:27.000Z","msg":"唔做有乜影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"有機會演變cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12b854a98633048e8db9febd931ba6e041ff13b","tid":665044,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bf9dd9a5fa9956aad9148943a7586b4b6176084","tid":665044,"uid":185792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48fe083e8bd0780c224a1fbe5c80a957f7347e74","tid":665044,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:09:27.000Z","msg":"唔做有乜影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"有機會演變cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:17:16.000Z","msg":"嘩咁緊係做"},{"pid":"b3af9f003257f915689f079401c33b6ca62825d6","tid":665044,"uid":19214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bf9dd9a5fa9956aad9148943a7586b4b6176084","tid":665044,"uid":185792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48fe083e8bd0780c224a1fbe5c80a957f7347e74","tid":665044,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:09:27.000Z","msg":"唔做有乜影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"有機會演變cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ae6a3df94bb64b324b99b1f96fd7c4ab76a032","tid":665044,"uid":39315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:19:27.000Z","msg":"我隻狗都係 但佢就一歲幾 前排都做左絕育拎埋隱藏果粒 其實都係睇隻狗隱果粒係咩位 有d會幾入下 就有d危險 上網睇過唔做的話 果粒野會易變腫榴 所以都係同佢做左"},{"pid":"f4f843c75e20f7428f70b3c9e5571ba683f46186","tid":665044,"uid":185792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6ae6a3df94bb64b324b99b1f96fd7c4ab76a032","tid":665044,"uid":39315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:19:27.000Z","msg":"我隻狗都係 但佢就一歲幾 前排都做左絕育拎埋隱藏果粒 其實都係睇隻狗隱果粒係咩位 有d會幾入下 就有d危險 上網睇過唔做的話 果粒野會易變腫榴 所以都係同佢做左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:27:14.000Z","msg":"我就係太後知後覺<br />\n而家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇完先識驚<br />\n咁都係先帶佢睇個好嘅獸醫<br />\n睇下隱左喺咩位先"}]}